wdi-DT.TDS.DECT.CD.def: Total debt service is the sum of principal repayments and interest actually paid in currency, goods, or services on long-term debt, interest paid on short-term debt, and repayments (repurchases and charges) to the IMF. Data are in current U.S. dollars.
wdi-DT.TDS.DECT.CD.name: Debt service on external debt
